Sunrise Session - September 2024 - Amazing Experience!!
Sep 2024 â€¢ Couples
We visited in September for the Sunrise Session, booking for our wedding anniversary. We booked whilst in the UK, waiting for our flight and the only space available was for a sofa on the â€˜sunriseâ€™ side of the building.
On arrival we joined the queue at the entrance (tip ask the taxi driver to drop you off at the St Regis Hotel, we got dropped at the shopping mall - which at 5.30am is pitch black).
The check in process was really swift and we were ushered up in the lift to the Aura reception. The lady on reception wished us a happy anniversary and said they had upgraded us to a day bed - which was a lovely, unexpected touch.
The view is amazing, easily the highlight of our stay in Dubai.
The pool and lounge area are beautifully clean.
The perfect place to watch the sunrise. The pool area got very busy as the sun came up but soon emptied out, as people went to have breakfast/sunbathe. Yes, there are lots of Instagram influencers but everyone was really friendly and offering to take photos for one another.
We opted to have breakfast - the truffle scrambled eggs were amazing, with a non-alcoholic blueberry mocktail on the side.
The staff were all really friendly and attentive, nothing was too much trouble. We met some really lovely people during our session.
The perfect start to our anniversary celebrations.
Will definitely return when we are next in Dubai.
Iâ€™d advise booking as far in advance as possible to ensure you get the seats/beds that you would like, as it gets booked up quickly.
Highly recommended.
